extends base

block content
  p Hi #{firstName},
  p Did you forget your password? Don't worry, you can reset it by clicking on the button below.
  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation' border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0')
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='left')
          table(role='presentation' border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}` target='_blank') Reset password
  p If you didn't forget your password or you did not register for our tool, you can safely ignore this e-mail.
  p Best luck!
  p EstiMate